While trying to work out who brought them there and why, they make a new home for themselves and encounter new friends, including Mo, the only other being from Earth â€“ a dinosaur.

episodes.overview: Elliott and his Mom, Frankie, investigate a mysterious rock which is not from Earth.

episodes.name: Wednesday (2)
episodes.overview: Somewhere across the universe, Elliott and Frankie discover a new place, and its strange inhabitants.

episodes.name: Wednesday (3)
episodes.overview: Elliott, Frankie and their new companion Mo find the strange new environment they're in isn't quite what it seems.

episodes.name: Idiosyncratic Introduction
episodes.overview: On Elliott's first day at the Hive, he meets the most unusual characters on his adventure so far.

episodes.name: Memory Mayhem
episodes.overview: Frankie tries to discover more about the mysterious rock that bought them to their new home, with the help of an entity called The Head.

episodes.name: Developing Dilemma
episodes.overview: Frankie lets Elliott get a pet, which doesn't go down well with their new neighbor.

episodes.name: Inadvertent Inversion
episodes.overview: As Elliott, Mo and Frankie all try something new at the Hive, they find their worlds are about to be turned upside down again.

episodes.name: Regurgitated Reminiscence
episodes.overview: Elliott and Mo go to great lengths to retrieve Frankie's old coffee machine.

episodes.name: Chaotic Clumping
episodes.overview: Elliott and Mo accidentally take a teleporter together and find themselves closer than they've ever been before. Will they decide to mutually part ways?

episodes.name: Parallel Paradox
episodes.overview: Elliott finds himself having to be in two places at once.

episodes.name: Problematic Prophecies
episodes.overview: Elliott and Mo make a new friend, Nara, who has a very special ability.

episodes.name: Temporal Tedium

episodes.name: Companion Confusion
episodes.overview: After a failed experiment in trying to find true love, Mo has to save Elliott from being sucked off the Centrium into outer space.

episodes.name: Melancholic Megalomaniac
episodes.overview: Elliott and Mo try to cheer up Lord Kallous, with the help of someone from his past.

episodes.name: Diminishing Discourse
episodes.overview: Elliott and Frankie decide to tell Mo about what really happened to the dinosaurs.
